race.comment: EXTRA ZERO (1) comes here third-up and ready to peak following a gutsy performance from the front over 1609m. Back in trip today doesn't look an issue and he has the speed to roll across and dictate the tempo. Can shed the maiden tag now. BLOOD SAINT (2) stepped out in trip last start and felt the pinch late, finishing 3.1L off the winner most recently. Back to this track and trip looks a good move following a strong performance here two starts ago. Draws a much better gate today and can land the knockout blow. NOBLE TOUCH (7) has shown good improvement her past couple and now gets the blinkers on for the first time. Needs some luck from out wide but looks to have found her groove her past couple and is not to be discounted. WINLOSEWEDRINKBOOZ (6) will find this a little easier than the two starts he's had thus far and can put his best foot forward. GOLD LIGHTNING (9) can improve now out in distance.
